description: Vite + React admin (frontend/) conventions
globs: frontend/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Admin frontend (Vite + React)

- Strict TypeScript; use `import type { ... }` for type-only imports when `verbatimModuleSyntax` is on.
- Functional components only. Prefer small page-level components.
- Call the API via `src/api.ts` (`apiFetch`, `login`); never hardcode the base URL (use `VITE_API_URL`).
- Admin routes require a superuser JWT; handle 401 by clearing the token and redirecting to `/login`.
